### 📝 Selected Publications &nbsp;<sub>(★ = first author)</sub>

- **★ ICASSP 2026** &nbsp;·&nbsp; `CCF-B`
  *Spiking Meets Causality: Efficient Granger Causal Discovery with Spiking Neural Networks*
  — First **causality-aware spiking attention** mechanism for efficient, low-energy causal discovery.

- **★ ICDM 2025** &nbsp;·&nbsp; `CCF-B` &nbsp;·&nbsp; **Oral**
  *DiffuGC: Diffusion Models Can Help Discover Granger Causality from Observational & Interventional Time Series*
  — Recasts **diffusion models as causal interventions** for a prior-free, intervention-based Granger paradigm.

- **★ WSDM 2025** &nbsp;·&nbsp; `CCF-B`
  *LLM-GC: Advancing Granger Causal Discovery from Time Series with Multimodal Language Modeling*
  — First to explore **four LLM paradigms** for time-series causal discovery; bidirectional retrieval-alignment; **SOTA on 6 datasets**.

- **★ DASFAA 2025** &nbsp;·&nbsp; `CCF-B`
  *From Knowledge to Causality: Self-Supervised Representation Learning for Granger Causal Discovery in Groups of Time Series*
  — **Knowledge-conditioned attention** that captures intra-group dynamics and inter-group interactions for group-level causal discovery.

- **Communications Engineering 2023** &nbsp;·&nbsp; *Nature Portfolio*
  *A General Aircraft Load Model through a Two-Phase Prediction Process with a Deep-Learning Multi-Model Architecture*
  — Core contributor. Attitude-partitioned two-phase framework reaching **97.16%** strain-prediction accuracy on **2M+** real flight records.

